  <brief_title>Electrophysiological Effects of Irbesartan in Patients With Paroxysmal Atrial Fibrillation (AF)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Electrophysiological Effects of Irbesartan in Patients With Paroxysmal Atrial Fibrillation (AF)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
