  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Recurrent PAF with indication for catheter ablation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Struct. Cardiopathy

          -  Mitral valve disease

          -  VEF&lt;40%

          -  Myocardiopathy

          -  LVH

          -  cardiac surgery

          -  AF reversible

          -  QT c&gt;450

          -  Recent MI/stroke, severe HTN

          -  Requirement of ACEI/ARBs

          -  Coronary synd., HTA, liver disease
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
